=== EVENT_SMUGGLER_OFFER ===
# id: 16
# title: Smuggler's Offer
# chinese_title: 走私交易
# category: Trading
# mode: starmap

A fast courier intercepts you with a business proposition: transport a sealed container to the next sector. No questions asked.

* [Accept the job]
  ~ gain_credits(30)
  接受 (jiēshòu) — accept
* [Open the container first]
  ~ gain_radical("口")
  打开 (dǎkāi) — open
* [Refuse and report the smuggler]
  ~ gain_credits(10)
  举报 (jǔbào) — report
